I found lying around.

256
00:14:00,340 --> 00:14:02,170
You tryin' to kill me, motherfucker?

257
00:14:02,250 --> 00:14:04,426
I'm not the one dousing
everything in salt, motherfucker.

258
00:14:04,510 --> 00:14:08,510
I pray every day that fire finds your body

259
00:14:08,590 --> 00:14:10,890
and finishes the job God didn't have

260
