If you could hear the look on my face,
you'd smell how sad I am.

262
00:14:15,600 --> 00:14:17,020
You watched anything good?

263
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:18,770
<i>Great British Bake Off.</i>

264
00:14:18,850 --> 00:14:20,230
Oh, goddamn.

265
00:14:20,310 --> 00:14:22,566
That show stood between me
and suicide for 10 years.

266
