Those are my feelings on
abortion, religious freedom,

267
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,530
animal rights, privacy rights, vaccines,

268
00:14:27,610 --> 00:14:29,860
free-market capitalism,
global climate change.

269
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:32,210
Yeah, duh-duh-duh.
No, no speaking lines, Buck.

270
00:14:32,740 --> 00:14:34,200
- Hi, Yukio.
- Hi, Wade.

271
00:14:34,910 --> 00:14:36,500
Nice fake o'clock shadow.

272
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:40,750
It's a summer balayage. From the French.

273
00:14:40,830 --> 00:14:44,210
It's meant to mimic
the natural highlights of the sun.

274
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:46,170
