- It's a hair system.

275
00:14:46,260 --> 00:14:47,930
I love your hair system, Wade.

276
00:14:48,010 --> 00:14:49,390
Thank you. Heh.

277
00:14:49,470 --> 00:14:50,970
Wanna do some cocaine?

278
